query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `avdVideoRecordings` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `processId` int NOT NULL,
  `employeeId` int NOT NULL,
  `stepNumber` int NOT NULL,
  `fileKey` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `fileUrl` varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
  `mimeType` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'video/webm',
  `fileSizeBytes` int,
  `durationSeconds` int,
  `status` enum('uploading','processing','completed','failed') DEFAULT 'uploading' NOT NULL,
  `errorMessage` text,
  `transcription` text,
  `analysisResult` json,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `avdVideoRecordings_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
